title: Burial Discography  - Untrue + All EP's, LP
description:
This is my burial discography.

It includes his 2 albums, 4 12" Ep's, remixes, promos, radio rips, sets and compilation songs that are not icluded on his own label. The promo mix on Mary Anne hobbs of many new Burial tracks is included - the epic Kode9 20 min mix.

This is the largest torrent of Burial material on the internet, and contains every available track by burial.

Enjoy!
